# Cursor Project Rules

- Follow the existing project structure and naming conventions.
- Prioritize small, maintainable changes over broad rewrites.
- Read `.ai/plans/`, `.ai/rules.md`, and `.ai/skills/ACTIVE_SKILLS.md` when they exist before proposing complex changes.
- Treat `.ai/context/agent-context.md` as the portable session summary for cross-agent continuity.
